Sample Flask App

This uses flask-security, SQLAlchemy, reCaptcha, bcrypt a few more libraries.
We usually use a mysql database.

Steps : 

Clone this repo, remove the .git files using the following command so that you can push your new project to a different repo.

rm -rf `find ./ -type d -name .git`

Change the name, requirements, config according to your needs and start your new project!

To install the requirements do 

pip install -r requirements.txt

To run the app locally, do

python runserver.py

To deploy on server we reccommend using 'uWSGI' and 

Happy Coding!
